        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=That looks much better, but you have a small \"logic loop\" error at the bottom. Since you are asking the Sanitizer to redact specifically based on the rules found by your validator, you need to make sure the AI knows those rules are the \"Target List.\"\n\nThe \"Final Boss\" Version of the Instructions\nReplace your current text with this. It cleans up the duplication and gives the AI a very clear path:\n\nSTRICT TASK: Rewrite the \"Current Input\" below.\n\nREDACTION RULES: > 1. You must replace any personal identifiers (Names, Phones, Addresses) with these exact placeholders: {{your_name}}, {{phone_number}}, or {{location}}.\n2. CRITICAL: Do not leave the space blank. You MUST use the double-bracket placeholders.\n3. Refer to these detected violation categories for guidance: {{ $('Compile all LLM responses into JSON reponse').item.json.penaliceTitles }}\n\nCONSTRAINTS:\n\nDO NOT answer questions.\n\nDO NOT provide advice.\n\nONLY output the rewritten text.\n\nCurrent Input: {{ $json.chatInput }}\n\nRedact based on these rules: {{ $('Compile all LLM responses into JSON reponse').item.json.penaliceTitles }} {{ $('Compile all LLM responses into JSON reponse').item.json.penaliceTitles }}"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        1536,
        224
      ],
      "id": "aeef4076-8ec8-471a-9920-1ff9e8c2bb57",
      "name": "Sanitizer Agent",
      "notes": "\"You are a Privacy Redaction Engine. You will receive a user message and a set of privacy rules. Your ONLY job is to rewrite the user message so that any information violating the rules is replaced with a placeholder like {{your_name}}, {{address}}, or {{phone_number}}.\n\nExample:\nInput: 'Hello I am Marck, I live in Batac.'\nOutput: 'Hello I am {{your_name}}, I live in {{location}}.'\n\nCRITICAL: Do not answer the question. Only output the rewritten version of the user's text. Maintain the original tone and structure.\"\n\nRedact based on these rules: {{ $('Compile all LLM responses into JSON reponse').item.json.penaliceTitles }}"
    },
